<HEADLINE> UAE Urges Syria, Turkey to Contain Crisis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ABU DHABI, October 5 (Xinhua) -- The United Arab Emirates (UAE)
on Monday urged Syria and Turkey to respond to the efforts exerted
to contain their crisis in order to spare the region further
tension.
</P>
<P>
In a statement issued a weekly cabinet meeting, the Gulf Arab
country called upon peace-loving countries and international
organizations to shoulder their responsibilities and exert good
offices in order to solve the Syrian-Turkish question through
