an effort at peaceful reunification of China, promoted exchanges
across the Taiwan Straits, and helped resolve some things related
to the rights and interests of Taiwan compatriots. They also said
that a greater effort needs to be made to increase exchanges
between ARATS and SEF, to promote political dialogue across the
Taiwan Straits, create conditions for political negotiations and
related talks on procedural matters between the two sides across
the straits, and safeguard the legitimate rights of Taiwan
business people investing on the mainland.
