<HEADLINE> Mubarak Arrives in Ankara to Mediate Between </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, October 6 (Xinhua) -- Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak
arrived here Tuesday afternoon on a mission designed to contain
the on-going crisis between Turkey and Syria, Egyptian Foreign
Minister Amr Moussa said.
</P>
<P>
Speaking to reporters at the Ankara Eseboga Airport, Moussa,
who is accompanying the president, said that "We have come to
Ankara to discuss the crisis between Turkey and Syria."
