<P>
Immediately after the arrival, Mubarak and his Turkish
counterpart Suleyman Demirel held talks at the Canakaya
presidential palace on how to defuse the mounting tensions.
</P>
<P>
Strained ties between Turkey and Syria deteriorated in recent
days. Turkey accused Syria of aiding Kurdish rebels fighting for
autonomy in southeast Turkey, while Syria bridled at Turkey's
growing military links with Israel.
</P>
<P>
