China's signing of the International Covenant on Civil and
Political Rights (ICCPR).
</P>
<P>
"China's signature of the ICCPR ... is a significant reflection
of its increasing commitment to the promotion and protection of
civil and political rights," Australian Foreign Minister Alexander
Downer said in a statement released Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
