<P>
QUITO, October 5 (Xinhua) -- Ecuador is looking for more
lucrative markets for its oil in 1999, and is especially targeting
Chile in South America, and California in the United States,
Patricio Ribadeneira, Ecuador's energy minister said on Monday.
</P>
