<HEADLINE> Chinese, British PMs Hold Talks in Beijing </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 6 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Premier Zhu Rongji held
talks with visiting British Prime Minister Tony Blair at the Great
Hall of the People here this morning.
</P>
