Statistics Bureau yesterday.
</P>
<P>
The number of small cities has increased substantially,
especially at the county level, with the eastern region
experiencing more rapid urbanization than the less developed
western region.
</P>
<P>
-- The General Office of the State Council and the United Front
Work Department of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of
