</P>
<P>
-- President Jiang Zemin, also general secretary of the
Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee, gave a basket of
flowers and a birthday cake to Xie Bingxin, a prominent Chinese
writer of children's books, to mark the 99th anniversary of her
birth.
</P>
<P>
-- An international symposium on eliminating iodine deficiency
disorders by the year 2000 opened in Beijing yesterday.
</P>
<P>
