series of measures to deal with "humanitarian matters" in Kosovo
and offer selfless aid to "all citizens" there.
</P>
<P>
He stressed that the Kosovo crisis can only be resolved by
political means.
</P>
<P>
He said he believed that the international community will
eventually stop pressuring and threatening his country and
contribute to a political solution. 
